{"tid":323180,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"外 籍 老 公 不 時 示 愛  李 蕙 敏 自 認 傳 統 感 怕 醜","createTime":"2017-07-15T11:54:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-16T07:08:36.000Z","uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"557d6694089b5f9c3b125bf149f257cbb54c6568","tid":323180,"uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T11:54:01.000Z","msg":"李蕙敏（Amanda）到電台宣傳新歌，透露新歌內容講都市人的曖昧關係，她認為愛對方應該講出來，笑言喜見近日有不少同性婚姻，為他們感到開心。<br />\n<br />\nAmanda自爆由於老公是西方人，不時對她示愛，但她生活在傳統家庭，中國人亦比較含蓄，加上本身性格較壓抑，有時又會覺得怕醜，故要繼續好好學習。她謂會多愛錫患腦退化症的母親，這樣做母親都覺開心。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20170712/_2017071213083324625.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20170712%2F_2017071213083324625.jpg&h=bacb5fae&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dab5e431cfa3d413187a0c7022d3c6737f939b44","tid":323180,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T12:08:28.000Z","msg":"當年紅過？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2eef5d6e831b5715d1559ddc6d7102d5197a4f4","tid":323180,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T12:13:11.000Z","msg":"係咪拍過9個女仔1隻鬼"},{"pid":"0ff7cdf7d1c821d26ed298376e54b263e7664700","tid":323180,"uid":77788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T20:44:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"847ace214c2a1a9087a9db1f8a4ec0ed848dbe1c","tid":323180,"uid":2260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T07:08:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}